Text.SourceString:
Scroll Lock: Show/Hide Cursor
Hold Ctrl: Temporarily show cursor

H: Show/Hide Settings

B: Create a new bot at aiming point
V: Create a new bot at current location
T: Set start location
(Shift+T: unset)

[Action Sequence Editing]
1: Insert "Waypoint"
2. Insert "Waypoint" (reverse drive)
3: Insert "Follow Other Bot"
4: Insert "Follow Current Player"
5: Insert "Drive In Circle" (Infinite)
6: Insert "Full Brake"
7: Insert "Change Seat"
8: Insert "Patrol"
9: Insert "Wait For Seconds"
0: Insert "Synchronizer"
J: Change Speed Limit for selected waypoint
